OL,3,CHundreds of homes issued 'do not
OL,4,Cdrink' notice by Thames Water
OL,6,F616 homes in Surrey have been told not
OL,7,Fto drink their tap water by Thames
OL,8,FWater.
OL,10,FThe supplier has warned households in
OL,11,FBramley, just south of Guildford, that
OL,12,Ftheir water contains higher levels of
OL,13,Fhydrocarbons, making it unsafe.
OL,15,FCustomers should not use their water
OL,16,Fsupply for drinking, cooking or
OL,17,Fbrushing their teeth, but they can
OL,18,Fcontinue to use the water to shower
OL,19,Fand wash hands.
