OL,3,CHundreds of homes issued 'do not
OL,4,Cdrink' notice by Thames Water
OL,6,FThe company said it will be delivering
OL,7,Fletters and bottled water to affected
OL,8,Fproperties throughout this evening and
OL,9,Ftomorrow.
OL,11,FThames Water has been regularly
OL,12,Fcollecting and assessing drinking
OL,13,Fwater samples in Bramley, following a
OL,14,Fhistorical fuel leak from the village
OL,15,Fpetrol station.
OL,17,FToday's testing showed a 'possible
OL,18,Fdeterioration in quality in some
OL,19,Fareas', but the company insists the
OL,20,Fwater was safe up until this point.
