OL,3,CHundreds of homes issued 'do not
OL,4,Cdrink' notice by Thames Water
OL,6,FTess Fayers, Operations Director for
OL,7,Fthe Thames Valley and Home Counties
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are asking 616 Bramley
OL,9,Fproperties not to drink the tap water
OL,10,Ffollowing recent water sampling
OL,11,Fresults.
OL,13,F"The health and safety of our
OL,14,Fcustomers is our number one priority,
OL,15,Fand we would like to reassure
OL,16,Fresidents that this is a precautionary
OL,17,Fmeasure. We are in the process of
OL,18,Fdelivering letters and bottled water
OL,19,Fto the affected properties.
