OL,3,CHundreds of homes issued 'do not
OL,4,Cdrink' notice by Thames Water
OL,6,F"We are also identifying locations to
OL,7,Fset up bottled water stations, and we
OL,8,Fwill share this information with our
OL,9,Fcustomers as soon as possible.
OL,11,F"We are already on site in the
OL,12,Fvillage, proactively replacing
OL,13,Fsections of our pipes on Horsham Road
OL,14,Fto reduce the risk to our customers."
OL,16,FA Waverley Borough Council
OL,17,Fspokesperson, said: "We are working
OL,18,Fclosely with Thames Water and other
OL,19,Fagencies to try and mitigate the
OL,20,Fimpact on residents, and we will
OL,21,Fsupport residents wherever possible."
