OL,6,FAn Asda spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fcontinuing to work closely with Thames
OL,8,FWater and other partners to address
OL,9,Fthe issues we inherited after
OL,10,Facquiring the Bramley PFS site. We
OL,11,Frecognise the impact this has had on
OL,12,Fthe residents of Bramley and share
OL,13,Ftheir frustrations. We are committed
OL,14,Fto working with all parties to resolve
OL,15,Fthis situation as quickly as possible."
